libhttpserver
------------------------------------------
libhttpserver is a small C++ library for embedding RESTful HTTP server
functionality into applications.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-2.8.0-1
  libgcc1-5.4.0-1
  libhttpserver0-0.13.0-1bl1
  libmicrohttpd-devel-0.9.52-1bl1
  libmicrohttpd12-0.9.52-1bl1
  libstdc++6-5.4.0-1
  pkg-config-0.29.1-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  autoconf-13-1
  automake-9-1
  binutils-2.25-4
  cygport-0.24.1-1
  gcc-core-5.4.0-1
  gcc-g++-5.4.0-1
  libtool-2.4.6-4
  make-4.2.1-2

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/etr/libhttpserver

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/etr/libhttpserver/archive/0.13.0.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack libhttpserver-0.13.0-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./libhttpserver-0.13.0-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/libhttpserver-0.13.0-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libhttpserver-0.13.0-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libhttpserver0-0.13.0-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libhttpserver-devel-0.13.0-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(libhttpserver)
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/libhttpserver.README
  /usr/share/doc/libhttpserver/AUTHORS
  /usr/share/doc/libhttpserver/ChangeLog
  /usr/share/doc/libhttpserver/LICENSE
  /usr/share/doc/libhttpserver/README.md

(libhttpserver0)
  /usr/bin/cyghttpserver-0.dll

(libhttpserver-devel)
  /usr/include/httpserver.hpp
  /usr/include/httpserver/binders.hpp
  /usr/include/httpserver/create_webserver.hpp
  /usr/include/httpserver/details/http_endpoint.hpp
  /usr/include/httpserver/http_request.hpp
  /usr/include/httpserver/http_resource.hpp
  /usr/include/httpserver/http_response.hpp
  /usr/include/httpserver/http_response_builder.hpp
  /usr/include/httpserver/http_utils.hpp
  /usr/include/httpserver/webserver.hpp
  /usr/include/httpserverpp
  /usr/lib/cmake/libhttpserver/FindLibHttpServer.cmake
  /usr/lib/libhttpserver.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/libhttpserver.pc

